{"tid":952832,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"助英軍再闖高峰 ,太陽報：卡尼將獲授勳","createTime":"2018-12-23T13:00:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T06:18:19.000Z","uid":30040,"like":7,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"366e664128962280bdba0f81f23b108567c11641","tid":952832,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T13:00:54.000Z","msg":"英格蘭28年來再一次打入世界盃四強，身為隊長的哈利卡尼居功至偉。英國《太陽報》報道，身為應屆世盃神射手的他即將獲英女皇親自頒授OBE勳銜，另英軍領隊修夫基亦在授勳名單之中。<br />\n報道指，卡尼以及修夫基已得悉即將獲授勳，但要三緘其口不能透露半點消息。卡尼的友人則指，卡尼得知消息之後非常興奮：「對於即將前往白金漢宮，卡尼受寵若驚，並且十分興奮。」卡尼俄羅斯世盃有出色的表現，更以六個入球獲封神射手，更有希望與碧咸、林伯特等英軍傳奇並列，獲得OBE勳銜的榮譽。"},{"pid":"fa15abca577f30f628773bd13fcdf7487c2401b2","tid":952832,"uid":57035,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T13:03:37.000Z","msg":"一次英超都未拎過就高過我地傳奇隊長MBE謝垃特?"},{"pid":"0ca0de406d22fca60afc12c34bfc7a7ae5cc6c4b","tid":952832,"uid":30040,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"fa15abca577f30f628773bd13fcdf7487c2401b2","tid":952832,"uid":57035,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T13:03:37.000Z","msg":"一次英超都未拎過就高過我地傳奇隊長MBE謝垃特?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T13:06:22.000Z","msg":"雖然好似好-6，但係你見到「幫英格蘭28年黎再次入世界盃4強」又好似合情合理。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f56c26c399155838dc7fc3ba3cf1701dac232ea7","tid":952832,"uid":192754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T13:08:59.000Z","msg":"已經勁過朗尼 奧雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_y.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90bd72476fa3e8fab94480e8a625b2e3d1f46e34","tid":952832,"uid":13391,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T13:17:33.000Z","msg":"OBE都claim到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78e6970b03a133609c3405ba9f1ec2808d165a78","tid":952832,"uid":36894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":